snippet.title: Monika Reads Your Fortune!!!! | DDLC MOD I Clay God Part 1
snippet.description:
This DDLC MODS gameplay is for Doki Doki Your Clay God. With Monika, Natsuki, Sayori, and Yuri in DDLC MOD style. Author's Synopsis: This is a mystery.

Before you is a set of cards. Every card holds a scene. Every card is a piece of the puzzle. The choice of which ones you flip is yours.

You will experience the scenes of this tale in a random order. By the end, all players will have the same information -- but the journey to them is bound to be different for everyone.

Mod Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RH-oIEHU4KDCg-tMGPvCHIUBhzvRudZk/view
